---
// MonicaMariageAd.astro
---

<div
  class="relative mt-[100px] flex flex-col items-center w-full max-w-md mx-auto overflow-hidden rounded-lg"
>
  <!-- Background image container using Cloudinary optimizations -->
  <div class="relative w-full h-[650px]">
    <!-- Préchargement de l'image principale -->

    <img
      src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dkbsvrpdc/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto:good,w_400/v1745254754/ylrvmsmxewylhvf6xywi.webp"
      alt="Robe de mariée"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-2"
      fetchpriority="high"
      width="400"
      height="500"
      loading="eager"
      decoding="async"
    />

    <!-- Beautiful overlay -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#a37b63]/30 via-transparent to-black/50 z-1"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Content overlay -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 z-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-between py-10 px-4"
    >
      <!-- Brand name -->
      <div class="text-center w-full mt-8">
        <h1
          class="mt-[100px] text-5xl text-white font-cormorant drop-shadow-lg"
        >
          MONICA
          <br />
          MARIAGE
        </h1>
      </div>

      <!-- Bottom content -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center w-full">
        <!-- See all button -->
        <a href="/robes-de-mariee">
          <button
            class="bg-white text-[#8a6d57] px-8 py-2 mt-[-320px] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-8 hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all shadow-md"
          >
            VOIR TOUT
          </button>
        </a>
        <!-- Opening info -->
        <p class="text-center text-[#5a4536] text-md mb-6">
          Spécialiste de la <strong>robe de mariée sur-mesure</strong> depuis 2014,
          MonicaMariage vous reçoit en <strong>showroom</strong> — découvrez nos
          collections <strong>princesse</strong>, <strong>bohème-chic</strong>, <strong
            >sirène</strong
          > et <strong>minimaliste</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
